information: TOM & EVA, a wholesaler based in Aubervilliers and specialising in leather gods, offers a wide range of handbags, backpacks, clutches and wallets. We manage the production process thanks to our special, direct links with the factories in China, giving you a substantial margin and consistently high-quality materials and design. Contact our sales department and showroom to discover our brand. As well as our yearly collections, we regularly offer new products to enable you to stand out from your competitors. Our models are featured on our website, which can be accessed by opening an account. In addition to our handbags, we offer a range of accessories including umbrellas and belts. Our products are intended for retail outlets, boutiques, resellers, semi-wholesale distributors, etc.
